title: Hanes Men's Work Socks, 6-Pack
description: COMFORT YOU DESERVE – Cushioned foot bottom for high-impact, all day comfort make these cushioned socks for men a sure bet for everyday wear, from work, play, gym, sports, and beyond.

EXTRA DURABLE – Our socks are made to be durable, but these socks are made to be Double Tough. During testing, these socks are able to withstand more than twice the number of rubs than our regular socks, making them extra resistant to holes!
SUPPORT YOU NEED – Compression arch and extra spandex give you the support and comfort you need
BREATHABLE – Knit-in ventilation panels allow your feet to breathe throughout the day.
KEEP YOUR COOL - Cool Comfort fabric wicks away moisture so your feet stay cool and dry all day.
FRESH ALL DAY - Fresh IQ advanced odor protection technology

Hanes Work Crew Socks, with Double Tough durability, work as hard as you do. Arch compression around the foot and extra spandex deliver a better fit. A fully cushioned foot bottom will keep you comfortable all day. Wicking Cool Comfort Fabric, combined with our FreshIQ Advanced Odor Protection, will help fight those stinky feet while keeping them cool and dry! Spandex and Comfort Toe Seam will provide comfort and a better fit.
